!                                                                      !
!  This subroutine reads and writes the coupling data streams between  !
!  ocean and wave models. Currently, the following data streams are    !
!  processed:                                                          !
!                                                                      !
!                                                                      !
!  Fields imported from the ATM Model:                                 !
!                                                                      !
